\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd\u003eUp to 16GB\u003c/td\u003e\u003c/tr\u003e\u003ctr\u003e\u003ctd\u003eStorage\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd\u003eUp to 256GB\u003c/td\u003e\u003c/tr\u003e\u003ctr\u003e\u003ctd\u003eBattery\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd\u003e60Wh, 65W Rapid Charge\u003c/td\u003e\u003c/tr\u003e\u003ctr\u003e\u003ctd\u003eUSB Ports\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd\u003e2 USB-C ports, 1 USB-A port\u003c/td\u003e\u003c/tr\u003e\u003ctr\u003e\u003ctd\u003eConnectivity\u003c/td\u003e\u003ctd\u003eBluetooth 5.4, Wi-Fi 7\u003c/td\u003e\u003c/tr\u003e\u003c/tbody\u003e\u003c/table\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" width=\"1151\" height=\"768\" src=\"https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/6_Lenovo-Chromebook-Plus-14.png\" alt=\"Lenovo\u0026#39;s New Chromebook Plus Might Be the Best One Yet 8\" srcset=\"https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/6_Lenovo-Chromebook-Plus-14.png 1151w, https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/6_Lenovo-Chromebook-Plus-14-300x200.png 300w, https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/6_Lenovo-Chromebook-Plus-14-380x254.png 380w, https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/6_Lenovo-Chromebook-Plus-14-550x367.png 550w, https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/6_Lenovo-Chromebook-Plus-14-800x534.png 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1151px) 100vw, 1151px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20width=\u0026#39;1151\u0026#39;%20height=\u0026#39;768\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201151%20768\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-src=\"https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/6_Lenovo-Chromebook-Plus-14.png\" data-srcset=\"https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/6_Lenovo-Chromebook-Plus-14.png 1151w, https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/6_Lenovo-Chromebook-Plus-14-300x200.png 300w, https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/6_Lenovo-Chromebook-Plus-14-380x254.png 380w, https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/6_Lenovo-Chromebook-Plus-14-550x367.png 550w, https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/6_Lenovo-Chromebook-Plus-14-800x534.png 800w\"/\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003eImage: Lenovo\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe display is a 14-inch 2K OLED panel that covers 100% of the DCI-P3 color gamut, which makes it perfect for the creators in the crowd. It is also in a taller 16:10 aspect ratio, which favors multitasking.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch3 id=\"software-and-ai\"\u003eSoftware and AI\u003c/h3\u003e\n\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" width=\"2000\" height=\"1500\" src=\"https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Lenovo-Chromebook-Plus-14-4-2000x1500.jpg\" alt=\"Lenovo\u0026#39;s New Chromebook Plus Might Be the Best One Yet 9\" srcset=\"https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Lenovo-Chromebook-Plus-14-4-2000x1500.jpg 2000w, https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Lenovo-Chromebook-Plus-14-4-1300x975.jpg 1300w, https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Lenovo-Chromebook-Plus-14-4-267x200.jpg 267w, https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Lenovo-Chromebook-Plus-14-4-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Lenovo-Chromebook-Plus-14-4-scaled.jpg 2048w, https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Lenovo-Chromebook-Plus-14-4-300x225.jpg 300w, https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Lenovo-Chromebook-Plus-14-4-380x285.jpg 380w, https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Lenovo-Chromebook-Plus-14-4-550x413.jpg 550w, https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Lenovo-Chromebook-Plus-14-4-800x600.jpg 800w, https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Lenovo-Chromebook-Plus-14-4-1160x870.jpg 1160w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20width=\u0026#39;2000\u0026#39;%20height=\u0026#39;1500\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%202000%201500\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-src=\"https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Lenovo-Chromebook-Plus-14-4-2000x1500.jpg\" data-srcset=\"https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Lenovo-Chromebook-Plus-14-4-2000x1500.jpg 2000w, https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Lenovo-Chromebook-Plus-14-4-1300x975.jpg 1300w, https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Lenovo-Chromebook-Plus-14-4-267x200.jpg 267w, https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Lenovo-Chromebook-Plus-14-4-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Lenovo-Chromebook-Plus-14-4-scaled.jpg 2048w, https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Lenovo-Chromebook-Plus-14-4-300x225.jpg 300w, https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Lenovo-Chromebook-Plus-14-4-380x285.jpg 380w, https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Lenovo-Chromebook-Plus-14-4-550x413.jpg 550w, https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Lenovo-Chromebook-Plus-14-4-800x600.jpg 800w, https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/Lenovo-Chromebook-Plus-14-4-1160x870.jpg 1160w\"/\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003eImage: Lenovo\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\u003cp\u003eUnsurprisingly, the Chromebook Plus 14 runs on \u003ca href=\"https://www.talkandroid.com/482834-chrome-os-126-update/\" target=\"_blank\" data-type=\"link\" data-id=\"https://www.talkandroid.com/482834-chrome-os-126-update/\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" data-wpel-link=\"internal\"\u003eChrome OS\u003c/a\u003e, and Google\u0026#39;s influence means that you can expect to see a lot of AI magic, especially with a capable NPU onboard. Google AI is built into the OS, providing features like:\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eSmart Grouping, to organize tabs, apps, and documents, even offline\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003eImage Editing, in the gallery app, even without an internet connection\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003eSelect to Search, uses Lens to search up anything on your screen\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003eText Capture to identify text from documents, photos, and emails, and add them to your Calendar or other apps\u003c/li\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cli\u003eHelp Me Read, summarizes text and even quizzes you to help with retention\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch3 id=\"pricing-and-availability\"\u003ePricing and Availability\u003c/h3\u003e\n\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg decoding=\"async\" width=\"1152\" height=\"768\" src=\"https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/2_Lenovo-Chromebook-Plus-14.png\" alt=\"Lenovo\u0026#39;s New Chromebook Plus Might Be the Best One Yet 10\" srcset=\"https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/2_Lenovo-Chromebook-Plus-14.png 1152w, https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/2_Lenovo-Chromebook-Plus-14-300x200.png 300w, https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/2_Lenovo-Chromebook-Plus-14-380x253.png 380w, https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/2_Lenovo-Chromebook-Plus-14-550x367.png 550w, https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/2_Lenovo-Chromebook-Plus-14-800x533.png 800w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1152px) 100vw, 1152px\" data-old-src=\"data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg%20xmlns=\u0026#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\u0026#39;%20width=\u0026#39;1152\u0026#39;%20height=\u0026#39;768\u0026#39;%20viewBox=\u0026#39;0%200%201152%20768\u0026#39;%3E%3C/svg%3E\" data-src=\"https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/2_Lenovo-Chromebook-Plus-14.png\" data-srcset=\"https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/2_Lenovo-Chromebook-Plus-14.png 1152w, https://www.talkandroid.com/wp-conten